phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.arky_world: §2<Unahzaal>: §rOh, the history of this world could have been great!
§2<Unahzaal>: §rBut I absorbed it before this world had a Guardian.
§2<Unahzaal>: §rAlas, this world is not destined for rescue.
§2<Unahzaal>: §rYou are doing well, Miguel could not pass the previous trial.
§2<Unahzaal>: §rI still have a job for him.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.dies.3: §2<Unahzaal>: §rYou didn't kill me, because it's impossible.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.dies.5: §2<Unahzaal>: §rAnd so I will leave your world.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.dies.7: §2<Unahzaal>: §rOne day you will be dead, because you are mortal.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.dies.8: §2<Unahzaal>: §rAnd no one else can stop me...
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.enter.3: §2<§kUnahzaal§r§2>: §rWhy mine? Soon you will know everything, wanderer...
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.enter.4: §2<§kUnahzaal§r§2>: §rFollow the path to find out why you are here, what is the meaning of your long journey through all these worlds.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.euca.1: §2<Unahzaal>: §rI am glad to see the eagerness with which you pass my trials.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.euca.2: §2<Unahzaal>: §rThe time has come to see the first world.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.euca.3: §2<Unahzaal>: §rThe ancient world. A very bright world.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.euca.6: §2<Unahzaal>: §rIt took a long time to capture it.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.euca.7: §2<Unahzaal>: §rIt fought back almost as hard as your world.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.final_room: §2<Unahzaal>: §rAlas for you, I feel the resistance in your heart.
§2<Unahzaal>: §rI feel  your rejection of my world.
§2<Unahzaal>: §rSo you have no right to stay here.
§2<Unahzaal>: §rCan you summon me? Can you figure out how to do it?
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.1: §2<§kUnahzaal§r§2>: §rMany billions of years ago, there was an explosion that gave birth to your home universe. I caught that event.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.10: §2<Unahzaal>: §rNothing in all the worlds, no library can compare to my knowledge of the multiverse.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.11: §2<Unahzaal>: §rIf you knew even one quadrillionth of what I know, your brain would explode from overload.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.12: §2<Unahzaal>: §rAs I said earlier, I am a curious god. But simply observing worlds, gathering information about them, is not enough.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.13: §2<Unahzaal>: §rIt is easiest when these worlds belong to you.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.14: §2<Unahzaal>: §rI have begun to collect them, to unite them with mine.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.15: §2<Unahzaal>: §rAnd thanks to you, your universe will join me.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.16: §2<Unahzaal>: §rYour home star system contained a vast array of deities and beings that could have thwarted me.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.17: §2<Unahzaal>: §rGulibeg, Enicrih, Xaxxas, Arahulum, Nyetet and others...
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.18: §2<Unahzaal>: §rBut now they are dead or weakened.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.2: §2<§kUnahzaal§r§2>: §rOriginally, it was already filled with billions of deities. From the weak like Vivid to the strongest, comparable to me.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.22: §2<Unahzaal>: §rI think you'll change your mind by the end of the journey...
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.23: §2<Unahzaal>: §rDo you want to see the worlds that I have already conquered?
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.24: §2<Unahzaal>: §rPass my trials, prove yourself worthy, show your loyalty to me and I'll let you see all my power.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.3: §2<§kUnahzaal§r§2>: §rAnd thanks to you, the strongest of them are all but gone.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.4: §2<§kUnahzaal§r§2>: §rAnd what is the essence of your journey?
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.6: §2<§kUnahzaal§r§2>: §rI am the God of Eternal Knowledge, known by innumerable names in many different worlds, but in yours my name is...
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.8: §2<Unahzaal>: §rI can't say exactly when I appeared, but I was originally a curious god.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.hallway.9: §2<Unahzaal>: §rWhich made me a god of knowledge.
phrase.eternal_tales.unahzaal.old_worlds: §2<Unahzaal>: §rOh, these are the oldest worlds I've ever captured.
§2<Unahzaal>: §rIt's been so long since I've visited them that they've blended together.
§2<Unahzaal>: §rThey are so ancient that no one remembers them anymore...
